I '''Sir Peter Paul Rubens''' ({{IPA-nl|ˈrybə(n)s}}; 28 Junio 1577 – 30 Mayo 1640), metung yang talapintang [[Flemish Baroque]], ampong talataguyud ning metung a "gastarul" (''extravagant'') a istilong [[Baroque]] a mititimid king kimut, kule, ampong sensualidad. Kilala ya kareng [[Counter-Reformation]] a [[altarpiece]], [[larawan]], [[Landscape painting|landscape]], ampong larawan ning amlat (history painting) da reng paksang ibat king mitolohiya ampong alegorya.  

Bukud king pamanibala king maragul a studio king [[Antwerp]] a maglalang pininturang sikat kareng aristokrata (nobility) ampo kareng pamitipun ning arte o kalalangan king mabilug a Europa, menigaral ya king klasika i Rubens a iskolar a humanista, talatipun arte, ampong diplomatikung gewa rang kabalyero o suging Felipe IV, Ari ning Espanya, ampong Charles I, Ari ning Inglaterra.

